description:
———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ————

Update March 12

  • Fixed all versions

  • Switched the primary download model from 7 GB to pruned fp16 2 GB model. Check the versions below to download other models.

  • Added following model variants

Pruned fp16 & fp32 / ema-only fp32 & fp16

Figured not everyone wants to download a 7 GB model. I have not tested them out yet, feel free to snatch a file and post your creations :)

Conversion done using the script located here (Web UI version available as well, for those interested)

  • Useful SD links added below the model information

Which model should you chose? Quick read on these

Pruned models & their differences

Fp32 & Fp16 & their differences

ema-only weights use less VRAM - suitable for inference

ema / no-ema weights use more VRAM - suitable for fine-tuning

Useful links for styles / prompting & other SD related things are posted under, just scroll to the bottom of the model info.

License updated in accordance to Chillout.

———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ————

MEOW MIX

This is my first merge, I was mostly interested in seeing how it works, completely random.

It work with pretty much everything, NSFW is decent. NSFW previews are last in the list.

This model produces rather realistic looking portraits, but with right prompts a lot can be achieved.

Preview images were made using no loras nor negative TIs. What you see is what you get. Used face restoration & hires fix, R-ESRGAN 4x+ with 0.4 denoise, 50 sampling steps. Face restore / hires fix is not necessary in most cases.

———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ————

What it contains

  • Chillout

  • F222

  • BasilticAbyssDream

  • Chillout Night

  • BlueberryMix

First merge had Moist VAE included. Second merge had a VAE file included as well, although I cannot quite remember which one it was.

———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ————

License

Chiliout license applies.

Since not everyone is happy with such a license, I will be trying to produce a similar merge without Chillout included, that is, if people are interested in this model. Do let me know how you feel about the model in the comments.

———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ———— ▬▬▬▬ ————

Have fun!
